WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:03.480
It is the one way to break Wenlock's spell.

00:03.480 --> 00:06.880
The Wand of Light has the most powerful magic of all.

00:06.880 --> 00:10.560
So powerful it overcomes all evil magic.

00:10.560 --> 00:12.960
It is built from a measure of courage,

00:12.960 --> 00:15.880
a ring of love, and a gem of ice,

00:15.880 --> 00:18.160
lit by hope's eternal flame.

